'''Walter Omar Kohan''' is Professor of [[Philosophy of Education]] at the [[State University of Rio de Janeiro]], Brazil. He is also a researcher at the [[National Council for Scientific and Technological Development]] (CNPQ) and the [[Carlos Chagas Filho]] Research Support Foundation (FAPERJ), and was previously President of the International Council of Philosophical Inquiry with Children (ICPIC).<ref name="Kohan 2015 p. ">{{cite book | last=Kohan | first=Walter | title=Childhood, education, and philosophy : new ideas for an old relationship | publisher=Routledge | publication-place=London New York | year=2015 | isbn=978-1-138-78797-1 | oclc=896848432 | page=}}</ref>

